After trim() â†’ "the sky  is blue"

After split("\\s+") â†’ ["the", "sky", "is", "blue"]

Reverse order â†’ ["blue", "is", "sky", "the"]

Join â†’ "blue is sky the"


âœ… Output â†’ "blue is sky the"


